      <title>越南和马来西亚寻求缓解南海紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vietnam-malaysia-seek-to-smooth-tensions-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在马来西亚的抗议加剧了南海争议水域的紧张局势后，越南和马来西亚同意提升关系并探索更紧密的合作以维护南海和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vietnam-malaysia-seek-to-smooth-tensions-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁迫在眉睫 中国总理将与外国企业首席执行官会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/chinese-premier-li-to-meet-foreign-ceos-as-trump-threat-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当企业准备应对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 提高中国产品关税的威胁时，中国国务院总理李强预计将于周一在北京举行的供应链博览会前会见外国企业高管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/chinese-premier-li-to-meet-foreign-ceos-as-trump-threat-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
